and global leader in promoting social equity through healthcare, education, and research.        Read about how UIC drives discovery            Saving the Monarch Butterfly    Posted on April 10, 2020             From the Theatre to the Hospital    Posted on April 03, 2020             Replaced by Robots? Not Yet    Posted on January 23, 2020             Chancellor Amiridis Celebrates Donors and Advocates for Supporting UIC    Posted on April 11, 2019             Chicago’s Only Medicinal Garden Adds Therapeutic Touch to Local Research    Nicole Cardos (WTTW)  |  Posted on October 03, 2018               TransUnion and UIC announce endowed professorship of data science    Posted on June 18, 2018             UIC launches fundraising campaign to raise $750 million    Sherri McGinnis Gonzalez  |  Posted on October 30, 2017             Honoring alumni for service, achievement    UIC News  |  Posted on October 04, 2017             $5M gift to expand nursing school’s simulation lab    Sam Hostettler  |  Posted on August 31, 2017             Turning Brownfields into "Greenfields"    Janice Cantieri  |  Posted on June 27, 2017                 Make Your Impact  Choose a fund on our secure giving form to support discovery at UIC.   Give Now            IGNITE:  The Campaign for UIC    Back to main content           Give Now    IGNITE Priorities     Support Student Success    Empower Faculty    Drive Discoveries    Connect to Communities    Support A College or Unit      Understanding Giving     Giving Strategies    Gift Planning    How to Give                    UIC Logo        Advancement       Contact   601 S. Morgan Street, 2503 University Hall (MC 002), Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: 312-413-8272  advance@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  U